description: PackStack PRO™ is a modular packing system designed to optimize pack storage, protection, and organization & keep your essential gear dry or isolate items that require safe storage away from moisture.
name: PackStack Pro 60L - Tall

specs.value: Fully seam-sealed. Cordura fabric. Waterproof YKK zipper --Do not submerge in water
Eliminates dead space in a backpack more efficiently than a packing cube
Enables easy access. Top handle also allows you to hang your PackStack PRO™
Store miscellaneous items. Can also be used to store your PackStack PRO™ when not in use
Option to combine and stack several units. Mix and match weatherproof and waterproof units as well as tall an short units
